query: SELECT f.id as fileId, f.filename, f.url, v.id as videoId, v.filename as videoFilename, v.fileId as videoFileId FROM files f LEFT JOIN videos v ON f.url = v.url WHERE f.filename LIKE '%snaptik%' OR v.filename LIKE '%snaptik%';
